{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.43\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"s\">流亡异乡者的祷告（二）</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.43.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>上帝啊，求你为我伸冤，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">向不虔诚的国为我辩护；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">求你救我脱离诡诈不义的人。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.43.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>你是作我保障的上帝，为何丢弃我呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">我为何因仇敌的欺压时常哀痛呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.43.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>求你发出你的亮光和信实，好引导我，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">带我到你的圣山，到你的居所！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.43.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>我就走到上帝的祭坛，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">到赐我喜乐的上帝那里。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\">上帝，我的上帝啊，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">我要弹琴称谢你！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.43.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>我的心哪，你为何忧闷？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">为何在我里面烦躁？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">应当仰望上帝，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">我还要称谢他，我当面的拯救，我的上帝。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}